Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.16,0:00:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾发生过战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.57,0:00:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后被称为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.80,0:00:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“极光战争”的这场战乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生在赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.60,0:00:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和茵费利亚之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.31,0:00:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赛雷斯提亚便断绝交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.82,0:00:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个世界面临即将灭亡的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出来拯救这场危机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是一群无名的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.74,0:02:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  那家伙朝岛的方向去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.04,0:02:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.84,0:02:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.51,0:02:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.62,0:02:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3话  狂风大作的南方之岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们消灭海豹应得的奖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.51,0:02:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就接受您的好意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来好像赚了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们暂时可以不愁吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.75,0:02:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对啊   法拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心没得吃的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有里德你这个贪吃鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.05,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.89,0:03:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后各位接下来有什么打算呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我们将照原定计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续我们的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了感谢你们拯救城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我尽点绵薄之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替你们安排住宿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们出发之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.94,0:03:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那旅管里消除旅途的疲劳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  啊  哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床好软哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒！  真是免费的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.45,0:03:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是领主大人交代的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这旅馆的老板娘普拉提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果各位有什么需要的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不必客气尽管告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有麻烦把蛋熊的培根肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.03,0:03:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和干史达伊姆装进这袋子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛   法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得可以吃免费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们吃丰盛点的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德你才在胡说八道些什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是得先作好旅行的准备吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不是为了玩才出来旅行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛也只是偶尔经过的一个点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有闲工夫悠哉享受啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也没必要这么急着赶路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就好好休息上一个礼拜嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行   明天就得出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.63,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了   刚好又有奖金入帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把旅行的装备换新才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂  我们去买东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德你们也分头去找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看有没有什么需要的东西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么…就是做旅行的准备啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要趁这时候能吃就尽量吃啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且还是吃免费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行期间净吃些储藏品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难正常摄取到营养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.19,0:04:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这个机会来吃点新鲜食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也并不为过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且还是吃免费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.66,0:04:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉你要不要也一起坐下来吃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是采购单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包  睡袋  换洗衣物  药品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及三双磨坏的鞋子都要换掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀剑送去磨一磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.60,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  也不用那么急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了   我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托先让我慢慢把饭吃完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的明白了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还是一样那么吵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.92,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.22,0:05:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你也在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就住在这家旅馆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.83,0:05:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你一定是跟在我们后面对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从昨天就住在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不准你埋伏偷袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这么的气势凌人呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.07,0:05:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行需要伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间是悲惨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要再多一点点的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是可爱的歌姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜·索鲁珍特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.75,0:05:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就让我来带领大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.65,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入梦的世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.02,0:05:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是大白天啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~   哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！里德大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经坎坷的一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定留下名垂青史的诗歌的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.61,0:06:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的吟游诗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德你认识他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道具屋…到底是在哪里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨我就是卖道具的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.73,0:06:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做蜜妮玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么要求的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会尽量办到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.74,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被绿意盎然的大自然所包围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像气候除了一年一次的台风之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是处处祥和的和平之岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行的商船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在航海途中停靠在此的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能尽情的享受假期呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.92,0:06:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过岛上的天气还真热呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳大成这副德行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.75,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让人失去干劲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这一顶要300G
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.86,0:06:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你觉得如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这顶不错  你还真机灵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来我口还有点渴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这是贝鲁卡椰子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是解渴的一大圣品呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好喝的样子耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个…要怎么喝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这是椰子切割器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.51,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备的还真周到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.61,0:07:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是做生意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是买了不少好东西哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  你仔细看这个哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以轻松的剪下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长在高处枝干的果实呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还附赠这个就算被坎培拉熊踩过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会坏掉的锅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在买的话只要1万G呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫做“只要”   拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.06,0:07:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上你认为我们有办法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背着这些破铜烂铁旅行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.57,0:07:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个卖东西的太会推销了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知不觉就给他买了这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会不买啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.94,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得基尔那边要不要紧哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快点看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一本历史书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到能找到这么珍贵的书籍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多么的幸运啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打开这本书籍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能更加磨练我们的晶灵学的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…你打算把那些全看完吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.79,0:08:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.60,0:08:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是这里面所有的书啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔你这个大笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不指望你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆我们自己准备算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.77,0:08:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎再度光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.63,0:09:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦  快一点呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.07,0:09:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.48,0:09:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜你也快点下来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.12,0:09:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下去了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.13,0:09:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢泼我水！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的回礼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天梅露蒂你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要去很远的地方了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.04,0:10:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟你们分开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好寂寞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.28,0:10:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才跟你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成好朋友的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂去拜托法拉好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拜托法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在这里再多待个几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们两个好像很开心的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德  基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.17,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你们把灾难带来的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的   不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.11,0:10:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得振作一点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个也一起下来游嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了   我们又不是小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.53,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔   一起下来游泳嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳这种活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会消耗大量的体力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.94,0:11:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为了消除疲劳才投宿旅馆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再因为游泳而累积疲劳的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就是本末倒置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德大人   下来游泳嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有完没完啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样  我已经受够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  你们就只知道玩乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.59,0:11:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是还在做重要的旅行耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有丝毫的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我们怠惰下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有也请你不要再来妨碍我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂  没必要说得那么过份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妨碍到你们了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.88,0:11:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光芒是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂   法拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要这么急着离开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…今天再停留个一晚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.61,0:12:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.91,0:12:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉提亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能不能请各位不要到外面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.59,0:12:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台风好像要来袭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台风？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为正处于台风行进的路线上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年一到了这个时节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会突然有强烈的暴风雨来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并给岛上带来莫大的灾害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过待再这旅馆里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没什么好担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.84,0:12:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们这建筑物非常坚固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以附近居民也都是来这里避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就麻烦你们啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.35,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然对方是天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下也无可奈何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暴风雨通过以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船也不会出海的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以出发的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能视情况而定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧？那怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到可莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  找不到可莉娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉提亚小姐  如果是他的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有看到他提着整理好的行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往镇外的山上走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么时候的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.88,0:13:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是下午的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他并不知道有台风要来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先问问看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.62,0:13:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有没有到其他地方去避难好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，他好像也没去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣法特教会那边避难的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.00,0:13:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.87,0:13:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去找他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.17,0:13:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂也去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂   法拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝你还是不要去吧  小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他往山上去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就已经来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.15,0:14:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击这个岛的台风速度都很快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一带每年都会发生山崩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是会被捲入危险中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那样的话就更非去不可啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要来妨碍我们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.38,0:14:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是普通的暴风雨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是要触她的霉头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是这岛上的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是最清楚不过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是鲁莽行动的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能会造成双重遇难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.53,0:14:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的关系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而害别人牺牲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.63,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.53,0:14:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.97,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好还是听听当地居民的话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.44,0:15:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这什么话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉提亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借我地图吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有对山路熟悉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.62,0:15:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双撞掌底破！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.47,0:15:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.61,0:15:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧我哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.94,0:15:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了   我们快走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.92,0:15:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.63,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾水之医治来保护汝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊弗力特西尔夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾之炙热魔掌熔化为灰烬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空之风啊   降下来并化为龙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.32,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.15,0:16:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大晶灵哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多的水之晶灵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合至吾之手化为盾牌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数的风之晶灵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听吾之命令化为墙壁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要渡过那条桥的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.75,0:16:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量怎么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.69,0:17:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么搞得？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大晶灵的活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像突然消失了的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.45,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要紧？法拉里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉勉强强啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.30,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑住我们现在就把你们拉上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要设法撑到上面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…   玛萝妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了   玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们抓紧哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧   巴鲁沙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.35,0:19:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.03,0:19:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.74,0:19:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德  你们两个一起下来游泳嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧  我正累着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有适合陆地生活的肉体的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果进行水中的活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就生物学来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.39,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的行动是很没有效率…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快要淹死了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.77,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命…救命啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.94,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉…你是故意的对吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡在法拉心灵角落的疙瘩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也稍微解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗中活动想对他们不利的黑影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却聚集在此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.16,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待下回精彩好戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么城里起了一片骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.46,0:21:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想舒舒服服的看着天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，法拉和玛萝妮又吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回   女人们的大决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…海中试验是什么？


